welcome_message_body: Welcome to Kaukauna, a charming city known for its picturesque landscapes and friendly community. We hope you enjoy your stay and take the time to explore all that our city has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Outagamie County Airport offers a variety of amenities for travelers, including dining options and retail stores.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A is the smaller of the two concourses at Outagamie County Airport, primarily serving regional flights.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B is the larger of the two concourses at Outagamie County Airport, offering a variety of domestic and international flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport. Simply connect to the network and accept the terms and conditions to access.

terminals.name: Executive Terminal
